    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few small scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of any major wear or odors, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver that needs nothing but a new owner.",
      "price": 36000.0,
