    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major restoration project or a donor vehicle for parts. The engine struggles with significant oil leaks and frequent overheating, and the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It currently requires a jump-start to run and is not considered roadworthy in its present state.",
      "price": 3500.0,
